{
  "texts": [
    "Integration in physical agents such as robots could provide a more seamless gateway between LLM and the user.",
    "• Co-development of apps.",
    "As a note to tech developers, our survey showed the importance of co-developing solutions with the end user (both PwD and supporters) in the loop early.",
    "Otherwise one runs the risk of designing a solution that does not address the needs of PwD or is not usable in the light of their expertise and challenges in using such apps.",
    "Furthermore, the language used should not patronize PwD or diminish their agency or cognitive capacities."
  ]
}